# Customer Retention Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes customer purchasing behavior using the Online Retail II dataset. The goal is to identify customer retention patterns, repeat purchase behavior, customer churn, and revenue trends through Python, SQL, and Power BI.

---

## Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- SQL Server
- Power BI

---

